comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-02-18T18:03:38.258Z",cursor-maintainer,"Plan: docs-first update PRD/README to move keyword search from roadmap to implemented, then add deterministic keyword search command with ranking and tests before running linked pm test + pm test-all."
  "2026-02-18T18:04:43.179Z",cursor-maintainer,"Docs-first update complete: README and PRD now declare pm search keyword mode in implemented command surface, while semantic/hybrid, reindex, close, and delete remain roadmap work."
  "2026-02-18T18:19:26.331Z",cursor-maintainer,"Implementation complete: added pm search keyword command with deterministic scoring/sorting and list-like filters, wired CLI/help surface, updated README/PRD contracts, and added unit/integration coverage. Evidence: pm test pm-pmd --run passed both linked commands (coverage + targeted search tests) with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines. Regression evidence: pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 1800 --json passed totals items=5 linked_tests=17 passed=17 failed=0 skipped=0."
  "2026-04-03T11:55:45.386Z",codex-agent,"Mapped external-audit Issue 12: add deterministic tag suggestion/autocomplete flow to improve taxonomy consistency."
  "2026-04-03T11:59:30.180Z",codex-agent,"Wave3 scope: tag suggestion behavior should be advisory/autocomplete-only unless explicitly requested, preserving existing free-form tag writes."
